General.Name: Azure Minerals Ltd
General.Description: Azure Minerals Limited engages in the exploration of precious and base minerals in Australia. The company primarily explores for nickel, cobalt, gold, and copper deposits. Its flagship project is the Andover projects located in southeast Karratha. The company was incorporated in 2003 and is based in West Perth, Australia.
